<TEXT>
GOLD shares came under pressure and the sector index closed the session down
45, or 2.7 per cent, at 1,602. The industrials index shed 24 to 4,339 and
the overall index was off 35 at 3,734. De Beers ended R1.50 lower at R76.50.
