FFr629m to FFr300m between the two periods.
The group's property division continued to suffer, reporting a net loss of
FFr330m compared with a loss of FFr273m in the first half of 1992.
Construction losses increased more sharply, rising from FFr4m in the first
six months of last year to FFr139m this year. The holding and services
division raised net profits from FFr566m to FFr768m.
