</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Reflecting the continuing impact of moving the Heathrow operations to
Coventry and of recession, which reduced volumes and margins, Norman Hay,
the engineering group, suffered higher pre-tax losses of Pounds 677,000 for
the first half of 1993, against Pounds 393,000.
Turnover fell from Pounds 4.79m to Pounds 3.9m for the six months to June 30
