the poorly performing clothing and chamois division was being conducted.
A number of options, both internally and externally, were being considered.
Whatever was decided, it was likely that provisions would need to be made
which could materially affect the outcome for the year.
Turnover for the six months was Pounds 58.5m (Pounds 50.4m). Losses per
share worked through at 2.2p (earnings 3.6p). There is no dividend (0.5p).
