<HEADLINE>
FT  24 SEP 93 / IMF study warns of risks in Dollars 8,000bn derivatives
market
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By JOHN GAPPER, Banking Editor
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
A STRONG WARNING has been issued in an International Monetary Fund study
about risks in the Dollars 8,000bn (Pounds 5,195bn) markets in derivatives
such as futures contracts and currency and interest rate swaps.
It says many transactions are not fully understood by the senior managers of
